0Z","msg":"射呀!!!!!"},{"pid":"b745b19d733144c9e4ea03f062890024dbb56cd2","tid":1014430,"uid":32938,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T09:43:19.000Z","msg":"睇佢D訪問真係幾impressive<br />\n你感覺到佢真心為球會好 好愛曼聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0d2c4eae044d041547d39f7e3f66fa90adc5d9f","tid":1014430,"uid":85284,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T09:47:43.000Z","msg":"雖然我冇認真睇過佢執教後嘅曼聯<br />\n不過純粹個人感覺<br />\n個蜜月期可能唔會維持得太耐"},{"pid":"925152eb3526f095c6e5e9a17ce51cf22f3ad51a","tid":1014430,"uid":193217,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"e0d2c4eae044d041547d39f7e3f66fa90adc5d9f","tid":1014430,"uid":85284,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T09:47:43.000Z","msg":"雖然我冇認真睇過佢執教後嘅曼聯<br />\n不過純粹個人感覺<br />\n個蜜月期可能唔會維持得太耐"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T09:50:07.000Z","msg":"根本唔係密月期<br />\n係蘇斯克查識激發班球員潛能<br />\n擺返所有球員做自己善長既野<br />\n好似摩狗既曼咁.成隊波都係黑字<br />\n但蘇斯克查一上到黎.唔係黃字就係紅字<br />\n普巴仲要係長期紅箭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最重要係個心態變左.變返一支強隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}